2000-12-16  Jim Meyering  <meyering@lucent.com>

	* src/chown-core.c (uint_to_string): New function.
	(uid_to_name): Use it.
	(gid_to_name): Use it.
	Rename locals, user/group, to uid/gid.

	* src/chown-core.h (enum Change_status): Start with 1.

