	* src/sys2.h (IF_LINT): Define new macro.
	* src/df.c (main): Rename locals i and j.
	Use IF_LINT macro instead of #ifdef lint...

	* src/dd.c (parse_integer): Add `const' to char* parameter and
	add a separate `suffix' variable.

